"title": "6156: fall, of humanity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6156",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>On account of their relation to Adam, all human beings have an inherent bias towards evil due to sin. Individual acts of sin reflect this bias, often referred to as “original sin”.</p>\n<h2>All human beings, except for Jesus Christ, are sinful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:11-Gen6:12\">GEN 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1-Ps14:3\">PSA 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:5\">PSA 51:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6-Isa64:7\">ISA 64:6–64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:7\">JHN 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:9-Rom3:20\">ROM 3:9–3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:12–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">EPH 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h2>Every part of a person is affected by sin</h2>\n<h3>The heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:21\">GEN 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:28\">1SA 17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:14\">2CH 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18\">PSA 66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:23\">JER 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:8\">MAT 15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></p>\n<h3>The body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:6\">ROM 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:12-Rom6:13\">ROM 6:12–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:13\">1CO 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a></p>\n<h3>Human nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:8\">ROM 8:5–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:5\">ROM 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:5\">1CO 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:21\">GAL 5:19–5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:8\">GAL 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are warned not to fall from grace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12-Heb3:14\">HEB 3:12–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:12-Matt24:13\">MAT 24:12–24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:4\">GAL 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:11\">HEB 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:15\">HEB 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17\">2PE 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:4-Rev2:5\">REV 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>God is able to keep believers from falling</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:14-Job33:18\">JOB 33:14–33:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25\">ROM 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1JN 5:18</a></p>",
